Label the centre of the spiral as the origin (0,0).  
Moving clockwise we get

1  at (0,0)  
2  at (1,0)  
3  at (1,1)  
4  at (0,1) … etc.

For a square “ring” k (k = 0,1,2,…)  
• its side length is 2k+1  
• its largest number is (2k+1)², found at the bottom-right corner (k, −k)  
• the first number in the ring is (2k−1)²+1 and lies at (k, 1−k) (one step east of the previous ring).

--------------------------------------------------------------------
Locate 2026
--------------------------------------------------------------------
45² = 2025 < 2026 < 47² = 2209,  
so 2026 lies in ring k = 23 (side 47).

Start of ring k = 23 : (23, −22) with value 2026.  
Hence 2026 is at the coordinate (23, −22).

--------------------------------------------------------------------
Find the eight neighbours
--------------------------------------------------------------------
Neighbour coordinates (x,y) around (23, −22):

(22, −23)  (23, −23)  (24, −23)  
(22, −22)  (       )  (24, −22)  
(22, −21)  (23, −21)  (24, −21)

Compute each value with the edge–offset rules of its ring.

1. (22, −23) : ring 23, bottom edge  
   offset = 6k + (x + k −1) = 138 + (22+23−1) = 182  
   value = 2026 + 182 = 2208

2. (23, −23) : ring 23, bottom-right corner  
   offset = 183  
   value = 2026 + 183 = 2209

3. (24, −23) : ring 24, start of the next ring  
   value = (47)² + 1 = 2209 + 1 = 2210

4. (22, −22) : ring 22, bottom-right corner  
   value = (45)² = 2025

5. (24, −22) : ring 24, east edge, offset 1  
   value = 2210 + 1 = 2211

6. (22, −21) : ring 22, start of ring 22  
   value = (43)² + 1 = 1849 + 1 = 1850

7. (23, −21) : ring 23, east edge, offset 1  
   value = 2026 + 1 = 2027

8. (24, −21) : ring 24, east edge, offset 2  
   value = 2210 + 2 = 2212

--------------------------------------------------------------------
Sum of the neighbours
--------------------------------------------------------------------
1850 + 2025 + 2027 + 2208 + 2209 + 2210 + 2211 + 2212
= 16 952

--------------------------------------------------------------------
Answer
--------------------------------------------------------------------
The sum of all eight neighbours of 2026 is 16 952.
